{"title":"三个青年农民的浪漫主义","authors":["王怀让"],"dates":[{"year":2002,"month":4,"day":4}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"三个青年农民的浪漫主义"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王怀让"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三个青年农民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在小镇上下馆子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们的酒饮得很少，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们的话却说得很多。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个小伙子把衣襟解开，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（他是全县闻名的小麦大王）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他显得无比自豪："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“有位诗人采访我，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我说我也是诗人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我种的小麦啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一垄垄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一畦畦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"整整齐齐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像不像一行一行唐诗？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丰收的时候，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我最喜欢扬场，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望着那漫天飞舞的金子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我当了一回李白，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我大声朗诵："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小麦之香天上来！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"另一个小伙子把袖管挽起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（他的菜园子上过画报）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他似乎有点骄傲："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“你的麦田是唐诗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的菜园是宋词。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄瓜句子长，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"茄子句子短，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青的红的小辣椒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正好作标点。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"菠菜一地如梦令，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"西红柿挂出西江月，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"韭菜包饺子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"家家满庭芳……”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人家的“词”还没有填完，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"第三个小伙子急得站了起来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（他是建筑队的能人，人称工程师）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他说着比划着："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“你们猜我在干什么，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我在写小说——张家要我设计小楼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要红墙红顶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我说，行，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我给你写一部红楼梦；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李家要我设计小院，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"院子在池塘旁边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我说，好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我给你写一部水浒；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赵家要我设计宅子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连同他两个儿子的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我说，OK，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我给你写一部"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三国演义……”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为他们是名人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们的话被有心人录了音，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乡里的广播站，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一连播了三天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"编辑加的标题是："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三个青年农民的浪漫主义！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}